    "content": "Switch to the shared arena Time to race real humans. Back on the login screen:\nClick switch racer if you’re in a lobby, then choose ☁️ AWS ARENA Log in (same name works — arenas have separate player databases, so you’ll get a fresh persona here) Now every participant is in one shared world: the world chat on the right shows everyone joining, and the leaderboard is global.\nTournament time 🏁 Your instructor will organize groups. Suggested format:\nRound 1: pairs — both players pick the same track, queue 2P Round 2: threes — queue 3P (FlexMatch groups by track, so agree on the track first!) Finals: top finishers queue 4P on the hardest unlocked track Racing tips:\nKey Action ← / → (or A / D) change lane — one tap, one lane Space use held item: 🔥 nitro (speed boost) or 💣 bomb (drops behind you) Watch the world chat between races — match announcements show who’s racing whom, and the cyan debug lines show FlexMatch working in real time.\nCheckpoint ★ You’ve completed at least one multiplayer race on AWS ARENA against another participant. Check the LEADERBOARD — is your best time on the board?",
